verse_part: Bathsheba who had been the wife
can it be made salty again
who had been suffering from a hemorrhage
will they malign the members of
HAVE THE GOSPEL PREACHED TO THEM
and began to bow down before
it is for those for whom
with so much as a finger
he would have been on the alert
is not coming for a long time
about to go on a journey
who had received the two talents
as He reclined at the table
Jesus was reclining at the table
they began to keep watch over
You who are going to destroy
while they were on their way
